---
description: Rules for Manticore models, mapping, null safety, and response parsing
globs:
  - lib/models/**/*.dart
  - lib/services/manticore_search_service.dart
---

- `manticore_category.dart`, `manticore_product.dart`, and `manticore_search_result.dart` must remain model/parsing files only.
- Model changes must keep parsing resilient to nulls, missing fields, unexpected types, and partial payloads.
- Update mapping/parsing code and `manticore_search_service.dart` together.
- Avoid embedding transport or widget logic inside model files.
- Prefer explicit field mapping over fragile dynamic assumptions.
- When changing model shape, check downstream UI and service usage for breakage.
